* copy beefsploit/loadxmlrpc.rc into your metasploit dir
* under your metasploit tree, under lib/msf/core/rpc/ patch beefsploit/modules.rb.diff into modules.rb (hopefully this will get fixed in svn soon)
* edit loadxmlrpc.rc to choose a better password
* run ./msfconsole -r loadxmlrpc.rc
* return to your BeEF directory
* edit include/msf.inc.php and update it with the approriate values
* login, to BeEF and have fun
